    .MainApp__Theme__Picture3"""
  .MainApp__Reason
    %h2.MainApp__Reason__SubTitle
      FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
    %ul.MainApp__Reason__Lists
      %li.MainApp__Reason__Lists__List
